<p>Some of the issues were:</p>
<ul>
  <li>It used a model more complex than needed.</li>
  <li>The code format was a mess.</li>
  <li>Mismatch of target output and loss.</li>
</ul>

<p>It was the last one which is <em>super</em> tricky, but critical.  It‚Äôs a hard to catch bug which inaccurately reports high accuracy.  I‚Äôll discuss it more below, but it‚Äôs a trap I‚Äôve fallen into myself. Regardless of the issues, it was good jump-starter code, since we‚Äôve never worked with a CNN.</p>

